coder v0.0.0-devel

USAGE:
  coder exp open port [flags] <workspace> <port>

  Open a port on a workspace in the browser.

OPTIONS:
      --region string, $CODER_OPEN_APP_REGION (default: primary)
          Region to use when opening the port. By default, the primary Coder
          deployment is used.

———
Run `coder --help` for a list of global options.
